{"tid":1234542,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"可能唔岩聽，但民主派議員點解今次點解咁\"激進\"？","createTime":"2019-06-17T02:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T13:02:05.000Z","uid":137220,"like":6,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6b997bacc33e27ebaad79543790f6f84e9578f60","tid":1234542,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:43:52.000Z","msg":"睇到人吹奏&quot;鄺神&quot; 有感，好似以前高登仔吹奏温爺爺咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次好多泛民議員&quot;對抗&quot; 黑警，浮晒上面，言詞都激動過上次，我認同佢哋做咗場好戲 (影帝溫家寶都係差唔多) 唔通佢地開始認同勇武？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實只係死到臨頭先知驚，好似23條果時咁，如果通過左佢地一定係首當其衝， 個形勢好似係逼狗跳牆，今次唔出出盡奶力， 利用所有可以利用嘅嘢都唔得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔好咁善忘，泛民做過啲乜<br />\n篤灰拖後腳，賣港賣咗幾十年<br />\n<br />\n有義士做嘢就屌，做完嘢有成果就自己攞彩<br />\n<br />\n國民黨以前同共產黨合作係ok， 但千祈唔好唔記得共產黨本身都係個威脅， 就好似而家泛民咁"},{"pid":"74f27a62fc7d242354cd3b8846edfd8735f84133","tid":1234542,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:49:03.000Z","msg":"香港人唔好太善忘&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350fa6fc4cc04f7fce7409d108c7d482feac6073","tid":1234542,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:53:29.000Z","msg":"以前喺高登屌溫家寶做戲都係吸負評，唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b16644c10f573ffa83bf6c1bbf5dc2cab1453ab5","tid":1234542,"uid":59664,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:58:28.000Z","msg":"有做野嘅咪讚，洗唔洗whatsapp通知你先啊"},{"pid":"e5660cee0b49f68af31f5ed85c31700214e7705e","tid":1234542,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f1a8d9c0c57717f708e277575e894a77d8f80c","tid":1234542,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b16644c10f573ffa83bf6c1bbf5dc2cab1453ab5","tid":1234542,"uid":59664,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:58:28.000Z","msg":"有做野嘅咪讚，洗唔洗whatsapp通知你先